This command allows you to promote a fellow guild member.
I would suggest only using it if a player's level has
accidently been erased (autoload strings have been known to
corrupt), or for players who are extremely loyal to the guild.
This entails things like doing things for the guild for nothing,
donating objects to the guild, continually helping new members
or recruiting new members. This command is logged,
so be prepared to explain your actions upon questioning.
Only Alarian or the Senior Guildmaster can do this.
